<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>과학 한 모금 — 매일의 과학을 한 모금씩</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ siteDescription }}">
<link rel="icon" href="/assets/favicon.svg">
{% set ogType = "website" %}
{% include "seo.njk" %}
{% include "_style.njk" %}
</head>
<body>
<header class="site-head hero">
  <span class="brand-big">☕ 과학 한 모금</span>
  <p class="tagline">매일의 과학을 한 모금씩</p>
</header>

<main class="toc-wrap">
  <div class="toc-grid">
    {%- for post in collections.post | reverse %}
    <a class="toc-card" href="{{ post.url }}">
      <span class="cat">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
      <h2>{{ post.data.title }} {{ post.data.emoji }}</h2>
      <p>{{ post.data.deck }}</p>
      <time>{{ post.data.displayDate }}</time>
    </a>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>
</main>

<footer class="site-foot">
  <span>과학 한 모금 · 전시실 뒷방</span>
  <span>{{ collections.post | length }}편의 기사</span>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
